Steps To Create Conditional Column 12    3.  Create Jobtag_New column

      - (1) Click to  Dim_JRP_Tag table

      - (2) Click to column JobTags ---> Add Column ---> Conditional Column

      - (3) Name the column JobTag_New

      - (4) in the Column Name box choose the column JobTags

      - (5) In Value box type the name of the JobTag

      - (6) in Output box type the JobTag_New that the Jobtag belongs to

      - (7) Click Add Clause

      - (8) Repeat step (3) to (6)

     - (9) in Else box type OTHERS

     - (10) Click OK
